  <num>31-1112</num>
  <heading>Validity of agreements as secured transactions.</heading>
  <text>No filing of the premium finance agreement shall be necessary to perfect the validity of such agreement as a secured transaction as against creditors, subsequent purchasers, pledges, and encumbrances, successors, or assigns.</text>
